  <p align="left"><font size="2"><center><IMG SRC="http://users.pandora.be/TheAlliance/Mortalis/31-01-2005/divide_1.jpg"></center><P><I><B><center><BR>A sundown in Great Divide.<BR>Awwwwwwwww. <BR></I></B></center><P><HR /><P><center><B>Back to business, </B><center><P><BR>We have been farming the usual stuff - CoA for augments, the odd Regicide in Riftseeker's (no need to post screenshots anymore until SoE gets that friggen particle effect in the King chamber fixed - read 'fixed' as in take it away!), some Epic 2.0 kills, a little Cragbeast Queen and GoD farming going on.<P>Ah yes, we found some mob in Mistmoore named Tyrian the Tormented right after the revamp, getting there took like 20 minutes for everyone, getting to the mob and killing it took like 10. Loot?<P><BR><center><IMG SRC="http://users.pandora.be/TheAlliance/Mortalis/31-01-2005/tyrant_legs_1.gif"</center><P><I><BR>Grats Carbonn.<BR>Talk of risk/reward...<BR></I><BR><HR /><P><center><B><BR>Some random snippets from /gu:<BR></B></center><P><center><IMG SRC="http://users.pandora.be/TheAlliance/Mortalis/31-01-2005/gu_crap_1.gif"</center><P><center><I><B><BR>By the way: We were talking about opening a bottle of wine.<BR></B></I></center><P><BR><center><B><BR>AFK motd:<BR></B></center><P><center><IMG SRC="http://users.pandora.be/TheAlliance/Mortalis/31-01-2005/afk_motd_1.gif"</center><P><BR><center><B><BR>And as a blatant ripoff of other guilds' &quot;The world of...&quot; <BR>series we present: <BR>Arfabel!<BR></B></center><P><B><BR><center><IMG SRC="http://users.pandora.be/TheAlliance/Mortalis/31-01-2005/arfa_0.gif"</center><BR>On it...<BR><center><IMG SRC="http://users.pandora.be/TheAlliance/Mortalis/31-01-2005/arfa_1.gif"</center><BR>BSE sighted in Bergen!<BR><center><IMG SRC="http://users.pandora.be/TheAlliance/Mortalis/31-01-2005/arfa_2.gif"</center><BR>EQ = browser game.<BR><center><IMG SRC="http://users.pandora.be/TheAlliance/Mortalis/31-01-2005/arfa_3.gif"</center><BR>Really, we wub joo!<BR><center><IMG SRC="http://users.pandora.be/TheAlliance/Mortalis/31-01-2005/arfa_4.gif"</center><BR>No need to, now the world knows.<BR></B><P><I><B><BR>Warriors and their buff slots:<BR><center><IMG SRC="http://users.pandora.be/TheAlliance/Mortalis/31-01-2005/sa_off_1.gif"</center><P>You see, it is easy to impress us during trial.<P>Which brings us to another issue:<P><HR /><P>Recruitment!<BR>Do you want to open this door? </I></B><P><BR><center><IMG SRC="http://users.pandora.be/TheAlliance/Mortalis/31-01-2005/mata_door_1.jpg"</center><P><center><I><B><BR>If you want to talk to our recruitment officers sent a tell to<BR>;tell venril.Guldren <BR><A 
HREF="http://forums.mortalis.com/forumdisplay.php?f=118">Visit our recruitment section!</A><P><UL>You can also reach them by email<BR><LI><A HREF="mailto:Guldren@skynet.be">Guldren@skynet.be</A><P></UL><BR></B></center></font></p>
